# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# NEXUS Campus Super-App — Environment Variables
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Copy this file to .env and fill in real values.
# NEVER commit .env to version control.
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── Global ──────────────────────────────────────────────
NODE_ENV=development
LOG_LEVEL=debug

# Comma-separated list of allowed institutional email domains
ALLOWED_EMAIL_DOMAINS=srmist.edu.in,srmap.edu.in

# ── Database (PostgreSQL + PostGIS) ─────────────────────
# Shared database URL for all Node.js services
DATABASE_URL=postgres://nexus:nexus_dev_secret@localhost:5432/nexus_dev

# ── Redis ───────────────────────────────────────────────
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379

# ── Kafka ───────────────────────────────────────────────
KAFKA_BROKERS=localhost:9092

# ── Elasticsearch ───────────────────────────────────────
ELASTICSEARCH_URL=http://localhost:9200

# ── MongoDB (notifications, analytics) ──────────────────
MONGODB_URL=mongodb://nexus:nexus_dev_secret@localhost:27017/nexus_dev?authSource=admin

# ── JWT Secrets ─────────────────────────────────────────
# Generate with: openssl rand -base64 64
JWT_ACCESS_SECRET=change-me-generate-with-openssl-rand-base64-64
JWT_REFRESH_SECRET=change-me-generate-with-openssl-rand-base64-64

# ── Razorpay (Payment Gateway) ─────────────────────────
RAZORPAY_KEY_ID=rzp_test_xxxxxxxxxxxx
RAZORPAY_KEY_SECRET=change-me-razorpay-key-secret
RAZORPAY_WEBHOOK_SECRET=change-me-razorpay-webhook-secret

# ── AWS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID=change-me-aws-access-key
AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=change-me-aws-secret-key
AWS_REGION=ap-south-1
AWS_S3_BUCKET=nexus-media-dev
AWS_SES_FROM_EMAIL=noreply@nexus.campus

# ── Firebase Cloud Messaging (Push Notifications) ──────
# Stringified JSON of Firebase service account credentials
FCM_SERVICE_ACCOUNT={"type":"service_account","project_id":"nexus-campus","private_key":"..."}

# ── Auth Service (port 3001) ────────────────────────────
AUTH_PORT=3001
AUTH_CORS_ORIGIN=http://localhost:3000,http://localhost:3100

# ── Bazaar Service (port 3002) ──────────────────────────
BAZAAR_PORT=3002
BAZAAR_CORS_ORIGIN=http://localhost:3000

# ── Wallet Service (port 3003) — Go ────────────────────
WALLET_PORT=3003
WALLET_DB_URL=postgres://nexus:nexus_dev_secret@localhost:5432/nexus_dev
WALLET_REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379

# ── Feast Service (port 3004) ───────────────────────────
FEAST_PORT=3004
FEAST_CORS_ORIGIN=http://localhost:3000

# ── Rides Service (port 3005) — Go ─────────────────────
RIDES_PORT=3005
RIDES_DB_URL=postgres://nexus:nexus_dev_secret@localhost:5432/nexus_dev
RIDES_REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379

# ── Swift Service (port 3006) ───────────────────────────
SWIFT_PORT=3006
SWIFT_CORS_ORIGIN=http://localhost:3000

# ── Skills Service (port 3007) ──────────────────────────
SKILLS_PORT=3007
SKILLS_CORS_ORIGIN=http://localhost:3000

# ── Pulse Service (port 3008) ───────────────────────────
PULSE_PORT=3008
PULSE_CORS_ORIGIN=http://localhost:3000

# ── Trust Service (port 3009) ───────────────────────────
TRUST_PORT=3009
TRUST_CORS_ORIGIN=http://localhost:3000

# ── Notifications Service (port 3010) ──────────────────
NOTIFICATIONS_PORT=3010
NOTIFICATIONS_CORS_ORIGIN=http://localhost:3000

# ── Search Service (port 3011) ─────────────────────────
SEARCH_PORT=3011
SEARCH_CORS_ORIGIN=http://localhost:3000

# ── Analytics Service (port 3012) — Python ─────────────
ANALYTICS_PORT=3012

# ── Admin Dashboard (port 3100) ────────────────────────
ADMIN_PORT=3100

# ── Kong API Gateway ───────────────────────────────────
# Kong proxy listens on 8000, admin API on 8001
KONG_PROXY_PORT=8000
KONG_ADMIN_PORT=8001
